  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/ee345bfbf522b12046208d48e6fc91ac.poster.avif?t=1773616933\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/ee345bfbf522b12046208d48e6fc91ac.webm?t=1773616933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/ee345bfbf522b12046208d48e6fc91ac.mp4?t=1773616933\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Slash, Shoot, Roll</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Phantom Relics</i></strong> is a fast-paced isometric slasher with real-time combat, deadly traps, and explosive action. Dive into ancient catacombs alone or with a friend in local co-op and stop the awakening of evil by battling through hordes of undead and powerful bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/65a1b70e99565593a47a75f13544bc8b.webp?t=1773616933\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore, Find, Think</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In search of powerful relics that may save the world, you’ll not only fight enemies but also solve puzzles, avoid traps, and explore the dark corners of the dungeons. But remember — each boss has its unique attacks and requires a special approach to strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/6e31ee1680035414208794093033a31e.poster.avif?t=1773616933\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/6e31ee1680035414208794093033a31e.webm?t=1773616933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/6e31ee1680035414208794093033a31e.mp4?t=1773616933\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔥 <strong>What Awaits You</strong>:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Brutal Combat</strong> — Chain combos, parry enemy strikes, and unleash powerful ultimate attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Firearms</strong> — Shoot with a shotgun or pistol; each character has their own unique weapon style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Traps and Explosions</strong> — Avoid deadly traps, use explosive barrels, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Local Co-op</strong> — Team up in local co-op on a single screen (<i><strong>or Remote Play Together</strong></i>). Two heroes — one cursed dungeon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Powerful Relics</strong> — Collect 15+ unique artifacts that change your playstyle and unlock new combat abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Epic Bosses</strong> — Fight powerful bosses, each with its own attacks and strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Dark Fantasy Atmosphere</strong> — Explore eerie catacombs, uncover secrets, and battle waves of undead, knights, and mutants.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/65a1b70e99565593a47a75f13544bc8b.webp?t=1773616933\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WHO IS THIS FOR?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>→ <strong>Fans of slashers</strong></i> where reaction and tactics matter. Prove that you're unbeatable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>→ <strong>Explorers</strong></i> – dive into a dark fantasy atmosphere and uncover the secrets of the catacombs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>→ <strong>Co-op maniacs</strong></i> – together, crush mobs, struggle with puzzles, share potions… and scream at each other.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/ee345bfbf522b12046208d48e6fc91ac.poster.avif?t=1773616933\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/ee345bfbf522b12046208d48e6fc91ac.webm?t=1773616933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/ee345bfbf522b12046208d48e6fc91ac.mp4?t=1773616933\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Slash, Shoot, Roll</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Phantom Relics</i></strong> is a fast-paced isometric slasher with real-time combat, deadly traps, and explosive action. Dive into ancient catacombs alone or with a friend in local co-op and stop the awakening of evil by battling through hordes of undead and powerful bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/65a1b70e99565593a47a75f13544bc8b.webp?t=1773616933\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore, Find, Think</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In search of powerful relics that may save the world, you’ll not only fight enemies but also solve puzzles, avoid traps, and explore the dark corners of the dungeons. But remember — each boss has its unique attacks and requires a special approach to strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/6e31ee1680035414208794093033a31e.poster.avif?t=1773616933\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/6e31ee1680035414208794093033a31e.webm?t=1773616933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/6e31ee1680035414208794093033a31e.mp4?t=1773616933\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔥 <strong>What Awaits You</strong>:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Brutal Combat</strong> — Chain combos, parry enemy strikes, and unleash powerful ultimate attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Firearms</strong> — Shoot with a shotgun or pistol; each character has their own unique weapon style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Traps and Explosions</strong> — Avoid deadly traps, use explosive barrels, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Local Co-op</strong> — Team up in local co-op on a single screen (<i><strong>or Remote Play Together</strong></i>). Two heroes — one cursed dungeon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Powerful Relics</strong> — Collect 15+ unique artifacts that change your playstyle and unlock new combat abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Epic Bosses</strong> — Fight powerful bosses, each with its own attacks and strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Dark Fantasy Atmosphere</strong> — Explore eerie catacombs, uncover secrets, and battle waves of undead, knights, and mutants.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/65a1b70e99565593a47a75f13544bc8b.webp?t=1773616933\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WHO IS THIS FOR?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>→ <strong>Fans of slashers</strong></i> where reaction and tactics matter. Prove that you're unbeatable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>→ <strong>Explorers</strong></i> – dive into a dark fantasy atmosphere and uncover the secrets of the catacombs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>→ <strong>Co-op maniacs</strong></i> – together, crush mobs, struggle with puzzles, share potions… and scream at each other.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
